The People of the State of Illinois ex rel. John S. Rusch, defendant in error, v. Harry Schwartz et al., plaintiffs in error.Gen. No. 33,654.

O’Connor, J., took no part in this decision.

Opinion filed March 17, 1930.Rehearing denied March 31, 1930.Nash & Ahern, for plaintiffs in error. John A. Swanson, State's Attorney, for defendant in error; Henry T. Chace, Jr., and Edward E. Wilson, Assistant State’s Attorneys, of counsel. Mr. Justice Matchett

delivered the opinion of the court.
